item.description: http://www.facebook.c... We'll meet at 10 a.m. at the Super Stop n' Shop parking lot, 137 Portsmouth Ave in Exeter (right off Exit 11 of Route 101). Thank you for all your support and lets cap Dr. Paul's career with his biggest accomplishment. The fight starts here in New Hampshire and ends in the White House. Those who are planning on attending please RSVP to Brian Early as soon as possible: briane@ronpaul2012.com or 603-769-0505.
